226
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,930
Sabi ng mama ni Momo yun lang daw ang paraan.

227
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,810
Akala ko namatay na talaga si Jin Ju,

228
00:17:49,970 --> 00:17:52,340
